import Main from '../layouts/main'
import Header from '../layouts/header'
import Body from '../layouts/body'

import Tabnavigation from '../layouts/tabnavigation'
import TabnavItem from '../layouts/tabnavitem'

function ExploreSpans() {
  return (
    <Main>
      <Header title='Spans'>
        <Tabnavigation>
          <TabnavItem>All Spans</TabnavItem>
          <TabnavItem>Saved Queries</TabnavItem>
          <TabnavItem>Suggested Queries</TabnavItem>
          </Tabnavigation>  
      </Header>
      <Body>Prefiltered span body</Body>
    </Main>
  )
}

export default ExploreSpans
